<h2><a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?id=749" title="Cheshire cat"> Cheshire cat</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


     

  	<p><strong>Cheshire cat</strong></p>

	<p>Sir John Tenniel&#8217;s drawing of the Cheshire cat grinning down at Alice is one of my favorites. However, the story as a whole always freaked me out.</p>

	<p>&#8220;The Cheshire Cat begins to fade away, his smile the last to go&#8221; </p>



 
