<div class="post-date">Oct  1</div>
<h2><a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?id=741" title="What I&#8217;m reading"> What I&#8217;m reading</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


     

  	<p><b>What I&#8217;m reading</b><br />
Star Trek: New Frontier &#8220;Gods Above&#8221;<br />
New Frontier is a great series that is independent from all the tv shows. Author Peter David has created a set of characters that are simply wonderful. Deep and very funny. Start with book one and work your way through.</p>

	<p><b>Tech I&#8217;m playing with</b><br />
I just got my wireless Internet up and running. No more hooking a phone cord into my laptop. I can now surf anywhere in our building. When I helped a local denist with his Macs he gave me the base station for free ($200 value-wow). Today I bought the card for the laptop. It works great.</p>

	<p>Also, I&#8217;m playing with an rss/xml news reader. interesting.</p>

	<p>Spent the day in Louisville shopping for clothes. I&#8217;m set for fall, Darlene&#8217;s still looking for shirts. It was nice to get out of town.</p>



 
<div class="line"></div>

<div class="smallcat">Posted in <a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/index.html?c=Culture">Culture</a></div>
